One GitHub repo can absolutely support DA Live, UE, and Google Docs — at the same time.
The constraint is per EDS project/site: one configured content source.
To mix all three, you create multiple EDS sites/projects that:
share the same GitHub repo for blocks and styling;
point to different content sources (AEM/UE, Google, DA).
