Authoring mode (DA / Docs / UE) is decoupled from delivery.
Edge Delivery + Adobe Managed CDN is what’s onboarded in Cloud Manager.
Once the Edge Delivery site is registered, any content source (DA, Docs, UE) feeding that site rides over the same Fastly‑backed Adobe Managed CDN.

