Phase 2 – Later, onboard that existing site into Cloud Manager

Once the customer has an EDS license and a Cloud Manager program with Edge Delivery enabled, you:

Open Cloud Manager → Program → Edge Delivery tab

Requires a program with the Edge Delivery entitlement. Introduction to Edge Delivery Services in Cloud Manager, Cloud Manager Self‑service access to Edge Delivery Services and Adobe Managed CDN
